I need some shoulder to lean upon
And a couple of arms to hold me

250
00:21:44,673 --> 00:21:48,063
Ain't there anyone here for love?

251
00:21:57,273 --> 00:22:04,065
I'm not in condition to wrestle

252
00:22:04,313 --> 00:22:08,272
I've never trained in a gym

253
00:22:10,033 --> 00:22:14,743
Show me a man who can nestle

254
00:22:14,953 --> 00:22:19,265
And I'll pin a medal on him

255
00:22:20,553 --> 00:22:24,910
Need some chappie to make me happy
And he don't have to be Hercules

256
00:22:25,153 --> 00:22:29,863
Don't anyone know about birds and bees?
Ain't there anyone here for love?

257
00:22:30,633 --> 00:22:34,672
Sweet love

258
00:22:34,873 --> 00:22:38,661
Ain't there anyone...

259
00:22:38,913 --> 00:22:42,872
...here for love?

260
00:22:48,753 --> 00:22:51,472
Doubles, anyone?

261
