Court's free.

262
00:23:03,873 --> 00:23:07,661
Two out of three, anyone?

263
00:23:13,073 --> 00:23:16,270
Doesn't anyone want to play?

264
00:23:17,153 --> 00:23:22,102
I like big muscles
And red corpuscles

265
00:23:22,353 --> 00:23:26,062
I like a beautiful hunk of man

266
00:23:26,313 --> 00:23:30,306
But I'm no physical culture fan

267
