Oh, dear.

784
01:04:22,633 --> 01:04:26,342
-Right over there, monsieur.
-Thank you.

785
01:04:26,833 --> 01:04:27,982
Lorelei?

786
01:04:28,913 --> 01:04:32,110
Hello. You remember
Mr. Esmond, don't you?

787
01:04:32,353 --> 01:04:33,422
Perfectly.

788
01:04:33,633 --> 01:04:37,706
Why not say hello?
He used to be a friend of ours.

789
01:04:37,913 --> 01:04:41,462
-Nice to see you again.
-Yes, indeed.

790
01:04:41,673 --> 01:04:44,983
Lorelei. Lorelei, wait!

791
01:04:45,193 --> 01:04:48,708
l've flown the Atlantic Ocean
to talk to you.

792
01:04:48,953 --> 01:04:53,504
-You can come in. lf you don't mind?
-l don't mind if you don't mind.

793
01:04:53,713 --> 01:04:56,671
-Mr. Esmond?
-Thank you.

794
01:04:58,553 --> 01:05:01,021
Aren't you even gonna
say you're sorry?

795
01:05:01,233 --> 01:05:07,263
l won't fall in love with a man who
won't trust me, no matter what l do.

796
01:05:07,513 --> 01:05:10,869
""No matter what--""?
That's being unreasonable.

797
01:05:11,113 --> 01:05:12,990
Well, goodbye, then.

798
01:05:13,193 --> 01:05:15,229
How can l trust you
after all Father's found out?

799
01:05:15,393 --> 01:05:16,508
(KNOCKlNG)

800
01:05:16,673 --> 01:05:20,461
-We're ready to dress you.
-Be right there.

801
01:05:20,913 --> 01:05:23,108
Lorelei, l--

802
01:05:23,313 --> 01:05:25,907
Men like you have made me
the way l am.

803
01:05:26,113 --> 01:05:30,311
lf you loved me at all,
you'd feel sorry for my troubles...

804
01:05:30,513 --> 01:05:36,065
...instead of holding them against me.
Don't say another word.

805
01:05:38,313 --> 01:05:40,224
l wasn't gonna say anything.

806
01:05:40,953 --> 01:05:46,311
You have a tough time. lf you want
to get upset, watch her next number.

807
01:05:46,513 --> 01:05:48,469
You mean....

808
