899
01:13:55,513 --> 01:13:59,711
-Until you finish customs--
-l want to speak with this gentleman.

900
01:13:59,913 --> 01:14:01,904
-Well?
-Have a nice trip?

901
01:14:02,113 --> 01:14:05,662
-My son, where is he?
-ln the café where the girls work.

902
01:14:05,873 --> 01:14:09,263
l explicitly told you
to stay with him.

903
01:14:09,473 --> 01:14:13,227
He can't be left alone
with that blonde man-trap.

904
01:14:13,433 --> 01:14:14,866
He's perfectly safe.

905
01:14:15,073 --> 01:14:20,352
Right now, the man-trap is in court
explaining things to the police.

906
01:14:20,553 --> 01:14:24,307
-That's better.
-We'll go when you're through customs.

907
01:14:24,513 --> 01:14:27,186
l'll be right with you.

908
01:14:33,513 --> 01:14:36,152
l beg your pardon.

909
01:14:36,913 --> 01:14:39,711
Sir Beekman.
l heard you'd gone to Africa.

910
01:14:39,913 --> 01:14:44,031
What'd you say? My name is
not Beekman, l'm Amos Finch.

911
01:14:44,233 --> 01:14:45,427
All right.

912
01:14:45,633 --> 01:14:49,421
Don't be in such a rush.
You're the chap on the boat?

913
01:14:49,633 --> 01:14:50,622
l am.

914
01:14:51,153 --> 01:14:54,623
-l was joking. Of course l'm Beekman.
-You're sure?

915
01:14:54,833 --> 01:14:59,588
My plane leaves in an hour.
Do you know where to find Miss Lee?

916
01:14:59,793 --> 01:15:03,991
-l think so.
-Give her a message after l've gone.

917
01:15:04,193 --> 01:15:09,904
Tell her that l had no choice.
What l did, l had to do.

918
01:15:10,113 --> 01:15:13,264
She'd understand
if she knew my wife.

919
01:15:13,473 --> 01:15:16,112
Tell her l know money
means nothing to her.

920
01:15:16,353 --> 01:15:19,663
-But l'll make it up to her.
-l'll tell her.

921
01:15:19,873 --> 01:15:24,264
Thanks awfully, old boy.
lt'll be a great favor.

922
01:15:24,473 --> 01:15:28,910
-All right, take me to this young lady.
-Yes, sir.

923
01:15:29,753 --> 01:15:36,101
(SPEAKS lN FRENCH)

924
01:15:37,473 --> 01:15:39,589
(SPEAKS lN FRENCH)

925
01:15:39,753 --> 01:15:44,110
(SPEAKS lN FRENCH)

926
01:16:00,593 --> 01:16:05,826
(SPEAKS lN FRENCH)

927
01:16:07,513 --> 01:16:12,143
-You will please swear, Miss Lee.
-Oh, judge, l never swear.

928
01:16:12,313 --> 01:16:17,626
Swear to tell nothing but the truth.
Will you do that?

929
01:16:17,993 --> 01:16:22,589
-Well, yeah. Thank you ever so.
-Sit down.

930
01:16:24,953 --> 01:16:29,902
You are being held for trial
for a charge of grand larceny.

931
01:16:30,113 --> 01:16:34,948
